00:05:31,300 --> 00:05:33,541
and Puzzle Fighter HD Remix with Capcom.

100
00:05:33,581 --> 00:05:36,002
So I have a long history with this game.

101
00:05:37,863 --> 00:05:38,964
But I don't have a long history

102
00:05:39,024 --> 00:05:41,666
or any history with Dominion or any connection to it.

