00:05:42,386 --> 00:05:43,827
It's just a game out there in the world.

104
00:05:44,047 --> 00:05:45,068
And some people said,

105
00:05:45,108 --> 00:05:47,029
hey, Serlin, you should really check out this card game.

106
00:05:47,899 --> 00:05:50,781
So I checked it out and I didn't really like it.

107
00:05:52,382 --> 00:05:54,624
What I did like is that you build your deck as you play

