00:06:31,651 --> 00:06:34,353
It was more that it was actually just my knee-jerk reaction.

123
00:06:34,413 --> 00:06:35,754
I said that sort of thing all the time.

124
00:06:36,635 --> 00:06:37,736
Years earlier, I worked on a...

125
00:06:38,496 --> 00:06:42,620
a third-person shooter, and it was like a third-person shooter that used puzzle fighter

