00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:48,345
mechanics. I also worked on a shmup, like a top-down shooter like Raiden DX, and again,

127
00:06:48,926 --> 00:06:53,250
let's get some back and forth from puzzle fighter in there. Now, neither of those games

